        &lt;h3&gt;Check Other Modalities&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;check-other-modalities&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#check-other-modalities&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Clarifying Your ‚ÄúOther‚Äù Symptom&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
    Does the additional symptom you experienced resemble a known aura modality
    (e.g., visual, sensory, speech, motor, brainstem, or retinal)?
